17:["$","section",null,{"id":"calculator","className":"border-t border-zinc-800 py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":["$","$L26",null,{}]}]}]
18:["$","section",null,{"className":"border-t border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl","children":"Stop calculating this every trip"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400","children":"OnTimer can automatically remind you when it's time to leave for events with locations — flights, meetings, appointments, and more. No more doing the math yourself before every trip."}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-3","children":[["$","li","Time-to-Leave alerts based on real travel time and traffic",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"✓"}],"Time-to-Leave alerts based on real travel time and traffic"]}],["$","li","Connects to Google Calendar and Microsoft Outlook",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"✓"}],"Connects to Google Calendar and Microsoft Outlook"]}],["$","li","Works for flights, meetings, appointments — any event with a location",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"✓"}],"Works for flights, meetings, appointments — any event with a location"]}],["$","li","Customizable lead time and buffer settings",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"✓"}],"Customizable lead time and buffer settings"]}],["$","li","iPhone app — alarms that actually get your attention",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"✓"}],"iPhone app — alarms that actually get your attention"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":["$","$L7",null,{"size":"lg","location":"airport_calculator_conversion"}]}]]}]}]
19:["$","section",null,{"className":"py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl","children":"When should you leave for the airport?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"There is no single right answer, but there are a few factors that always matter: whether you're flying domestic or international, how long security will take, whether you're checking a bag, and how long the drive actually is at the time you're leaving."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Most people underestimate at least one of these. They check traffic on Google Maps and assume a 35-minute drive, but forget that they're leaving during rush hour, need to find parking, and still have to get through a bag drop line. The math compounds quickly."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"A reliable estimate works backwards from your departure time: subtract the airport arrival buffer first, then subtract travel time. The result is the latest reasonable moment to walk out the door. The calculator above automates that math."}]]}]]}]}]
1a:["$","section",null,{"className":"border-t border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl","children":"How early should you arrive at the airport?"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"The TSA and most major airlines recommend the following as a starting point:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","Domestic flights: arrive 2 hours before departure",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"•"}],"Domestic flights: arrive 2 hours before departure"]}],["$","li","International flights: arrive 3 hours before departure",{"className":"flex items-start gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-500","children":"•"}],"International flights: arrive 3 hours before departure"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"These are starting points, not guarantees. A small regional airport with no lines is very different from a major hub on a holiday weekend. TSA PreCheck and Global Entry can meaningfully reduce security time. Checking a bag adds time at the counter and imposes hard cutoffs — most airlines stop accepting checked bags 30 to 45 minutes before departure."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When in doubt, add 15 minutes. Being early at an airport is an inconvenience. Missing your flight is expensive."}]]}]]}]}]
1b:["$","section",null,{"className":"py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl","children":"Why airport timing is harder than it looks"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Most people have a rough sense of how far the airport is. What they underestimate is how many places in the chain can absorb time unexpectedly."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Traffic changes. A drive that takes 30 minutes on Sunday morning takes 55 minutes on a Tuesday at 5 PM. If you pulled your estimate from earlier in the day, you may already be behind before you leave."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Parking adds time in ways that are easy to overlook. Finding a spot, waiting for the shuttle, riding to the terminal — economy parking at a major airport can easily absorb 20 to 30 minutes that most people do not budget for."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Bag check has a hard cutoff. Miss it and you lose your checked bag for the trip or miss the flight entirely. That cutoff does not care how close you are to the airport."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Security lines are unpredictable. TSA PreCheck helps. But even with PreCheck, a busy checkpoint or a slow line can add real minutes to your buffer."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The biggest factor is overconfidence. Most people who miss flights were not planning to cut it close. They just ran through the math too optimistically. A small buffer in every step of the chain is cheap insurance."}]]}]]}]}]
1c:["$","section",null,{"className":"border-t border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 py-20","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl","children":"A better way to avoid missing flights"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 space-y-4 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Calculating your leave time manually every trip works — until it doesn't. You forget, you rush, you underestimate. The math is not hard. The problem is remembering to do it, at the right moment, with the right inputs."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"OnTimer is an iPhone app designed to solve this automatically. For any calendar event with a location, it calculates when you need to leave and alerts you at the right time — based on travel time and traffic, not just a fixed reminder."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The same feature works for meetings, appointments, pickups, and anything else in your calendar with a location. You stop having to think about it. OnTimer handles the timing."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4","children":[["$","$L7",null,{"size":"lg","location":"airport_calculator_seo_cta"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/time-to-leave-reminders","className":"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-white","children":"How Time-to-Leave works →"}]]}]]}]}]
